<!doctype html>
<html>
{{> head }}
<body id="index">
  {{> header }}
  <div class="content">

    <section id="headline">
      <h1 class="headline">Locally sourced.</h1>
      <h2 class="blend">A peer-to-peer stack for building software together.</h2>
      <img class="headline-gif" src="../img/lan-party.gif" alt="">
    </section>

    <section id="get-the-app">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="email-signup">
          <p><strong>Sound fun?</strong> Join the mailing list to find out about future releases.</p>
          <form class="main-cta">
            <input type="text" placeholder="Enter your email"><button>Join</button>
          </form>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="horizontal-scroll-wrapper">
      <div class="horizontal-scroll-content"></div>
    </section>

    <section id="organic">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="druk"><span>Organic</span><br/>collaboration</h1>
        <h2>A new way to build software</h2>
        <img class="organic-gif" src="../img/extending-hands.gif" alt="">
        <div class="attributes">
          <div class="attribute">
            <div class="attribute-title">
              <div>
                <a href="/"><h4 class="active">No down-time.</h4></a>
                <a href="/"><h4>Everything is local</h4></a>
                <a href="/"><h4>Sustain open source</h4></a>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="attribute-features">
              <div>
                <p>{{> svg-feat-offline }} Offline-first collaboration</p>
                <p>{{> svg-feat-offline }} Available in every country</p>
                <p>{{> svg-feat-offline }} Peer-to-peer code sharing and hosting</p>
                <p>{{> svg-feat-offline }} Censorship-resistant</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="protocols">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>No more walled gardens.</h1>
        <h2>Built on open protocols, not platforms.</h2>
        <div class="image-links">
          <img class="protocol-gif" src="../img/garden.gif">
          <div class="links">
            <a href="/">source code</a>
            <a href="/">documentation</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="protocols">
          <div>
            <h3>git</h3>
            <p>something about git</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>Radicle Link</h3>
            <p>A peer-to-peer replication protocol for hosting & collaboration, built on Git.</p>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3>ethereum</h3>
            <p>something about ethereum</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="codelands">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Explore the codelands.</h1>
        <div class="two-column">
          <div class="two-column-item">
            <h3>Join the  Community</h3>
            <p>Everything is open-source and <a href="/">public by default</a>. Dive into <a href="/">our code</a> or check out <a href="/">radicle.community</a>.</p>
            <p>Drop in the #radicle channel on freenode</p>
          </div>
          <div class="two-column-item">
            <h3>Try out the beta</h3>
            <p>Interested in building Radicle into your code collaboration experience?</p>
            <a href="/">Download the beta</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

     <section id="timeline">
      <div class="container">
        <h1>Where we’re headed →</h1>
        <h2>To build a great product, we have to use it ourselves. We're building Radicle with our own tech. Read about our public by default strategy <a href="/">here</a>.</h2>
        <div class="timeline">
          <div class="timeline-item">
            <p class="here">We're here</p>
            <div class="icon">
              {{> svg-here }}
            </div>
            <p class="date">July 2020</p>
            <h3>Friends & Family</h3>
            <p>The core feature-set on top of a peer-to-peer stack. This is when we'll start using it ourselves.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item not-active">
            <p class="not-here">not here</p>
            <div class="icon">
              {{> svg-date-square }}
            </div>
            <p class="date">Late 2020</p>
            <h3>Public Beta</h3>
            <p>Everything a code collaboration tool needs including notifications, search, and discovery.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="timeline-item not-active">
            <p class="not-here">not here</p>
            <div class="icon last">
              {{> svg-date-square }}
            </div>
            <p class="date">Early 2021</p>
            <h3>Functional Release</h3>
            <p>The app will be hooked up with real money and the public registry and we’ll launch our native coin.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
  </div>{{! closes content }}
  {{> footer }}
</body>
</html>
